- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is a possibility as the paper discusses the inadequacy of existing corpora for conversational speech recognition. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possibility as the paper proposes a technique for constructing a training corpus and improving speech recognition system. 
- cs.SD (Signal Processing) is another possibility as the paper deals with processing audio signals.
